    "Evaluation loss reflects the average loglikelihood assigned to ground truth outputs, and accuracy indicates the model's ability to make correct predictions or produce exact answers.",
    "CommonsenseQA ResultsCommonsenseQA requires inference over world knowledge and context-rich prompts.DRaFT-Q consistently outperforms prior PEFT methods.",
